ExecDesc.value: Microsoft Word mso.dll LsCreateLine Memory Corruption (IPv6 Version)

EngDesc.value: There exists a memory corruption vulnerability in the dynamically-linked library mso.dll which is shipped with Microsoft Word. The flaw is caused by an improper check when processing data in Microsoft Word documents. An attacker may exploit this vulnerability to inject and execute arbitrary code in the security context of the currently logged in user. (IPv6 Version)
